dog trial stick
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a stick less than a metre in length that is used to prompt sheep or dog in a dog trial contest.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
